<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad"
>
  <body>
    
<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-about" />
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-details" />
</metal:leftportlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

      <h1>Bounties registered in Launchpad</h1>

    <p>
    In Launchpad, a bounty is an offer of payment
    for development work.
    <tal:block condition="request/lp:person">
      You can register bounties
      or sign up for bounties offered by other people.
    </tal:block>
    <tal:block condition="not: request/lp:person">
      <a href="+login">Log in</a>
      and you&#8217;ll be able to register bounties,
      or sign up for bounties offered by other people.
    </tal:block>
    </p>

  <table class="listing sortable" width="100%" id="bountylist">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Date</th>
        <th>Title</th>
        <th>USD Value<sup>*</sup></th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr tal:repeat="bounty context">
        <td tal:content="bounty/datecreated/fmt:date">
          date
        </td>
        <td><a tal:content="bounty/title/fmt:shorten/57"
               tal:attributes="href bounty/fmt:url">title</a></td>
        <td tal:content="bounty/usdvalue">usdvalue</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p><sup>*</sup> A bounty may include contributions in several currencies.
    This is an estimate of the bounty value in US dollars, based on recent
    exchange rates.
  </p>

</div>
</body>
</html>
